          </div>

          <h3>2. Strategic Location</h3>
          <p>Mississauga offers strong STR demand due to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Pearson Airport proximity:</strong> Business travelers, flight crews, and passengers with early flights</li>
            <li><strong>Corporate headquarters:</strong> Many Fortune 500 companies have offices in Mississauga</li>
            <li><strong>Square One:</strong> Major shopping and entertainment destination draws visitors</li>
            <li><strong>Easy Toronto access:</strong> Guests can visit Toronto while enjoying lower accommodation costs</li>
