          <h3>3. Flexibility</h3>
          <p>Unlike long-term leases, STR hosting gives you:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Ability to use your home during gaps between bookings</li>
            <li>Dynamic pricing to maximize revenue during peak demand</li>
            <li>No long-term tenant issues or eviction processes</li>
            <li>Control over who stays in your home</li>
